        li.h-AfterSquare.h-demo ol &gt; li.h-AfterSquare
        li.h-demo               ol &gt; li
    p.
      Use the #[code .h-AfterNewline] class to create a line break between items.
      Use #[code .h-AfterNewline-p] to do the same for #[code @media print] only.
